### Тестирование новых API endpoints (Фазы 6-10)
### Используйте REST Client extension в VS Code

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000/api
@token = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### ============================================
### ФАЗА 6: Settings API
### ============================================

### Получить налоговые настройки
GET {{baseUrl}}/settings/taxes/config
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Обновить налоговые настройки
PUT {{baseUrl}}/settings/taxes/config
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "default_tax_rate": 20,
  "tax_rates": [0, 10, 20],
  "tax_period": "monthly"
}

### Получить настройки синхронизации
GET {{baseUrl}}/settings/sync/config
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Получить категории (с иерархией)
GET {{baseUrl}}/categories
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================
### ФАЗА 7: Analytics API
### ============================================

### График продаж
GET {{baseUrl}}/analytics/sales-chart?startDate=2024-01-01&endDate=2024-12-31&groupBy=month
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Топ товары
GET {{baseUrl}}/analytics/top-products?limit=10&sortBy=revenue
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Производительность кассиров
GET {{baseUrl}}/analytics/cashier-performance?startDate=2024-01-01&endDate=2024-12-31
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Отчёт по складам
GET {{baseUrl}}/analytics/warehouse-report?startDate=2024-01-01&endDate=2024-12-31
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================
### ФАЗА 8: Notifications API
### ============================================

### Получить уведомления
GET {{baseUrl}}/notifications?limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Количество непрочитанных
GET {{baseUrl}}/notifications/unread-count
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Отметить как прочитанное
POST {{baseUrl}}/notifications/mark-read/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Получить подписки
GET {{baseUrl}}/notifications/subscriptions
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Тестовое email уведомление
POST {{baseUrl}}/notifications/test-email
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================
### ФАЗА 9: Warehouse API
### ============================================

### Создать оприходование
POST {{baseUrl}}/warehouse/receipt
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "warehouseId": 1,
  "items": [
    {
      "productId": 1,
      "quantity": 100,
      "costPrice": 1500,
      "batchNumber": "BATCH-001"
    }
  ],
  "notes": "Тестовое оприходование"
}

### Создать списание
POST {{baseUrl}}/warehouse/write-off
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "warehouseId": 1,
  "items": [
    {
      "productId": 1,
      "quantity": 5
    }
  ],
  "reason": "Испорченный товар"
}

### Создать перемещение
POST {{baseUrl}}/warehouse/transfer
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "warehouseFromId": 1,
  "warehouseToId": 2,
  "items": [
    {
      "productId": 1,
      "quantity": 10
    }
  ],
  "reason": "Перемещение на другой склад"
}

### Провести документ
POST {{baseUrl}}/warehouse/confirm/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Получить остатки
GET {{baseUrl}}/warehouse/stock-balance?warehouseId=1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Получить движения
GET {{baseUrl}}/warehouse/movements?productId=1&limit=50
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Получить список документов
GET {{baseUrl}}/warehouse/documents?type=receipt&status=confirmed
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================
### ФАЗА 10: Finance API
### ============================================

### Детализированный P&L
GET {{baseUrl}}/finance/profit-loss-detailed?startDate=2024-01-01&endDate=2024-12-31
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Cash Flow
GET {{baseUrl}}/finance/cash-flow?startDate=2024-01-01&endDate=2024-12-31
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Анализ рентабельности
GET {{baseUrl}}/finance/profitability?startDate=2024-01-01&endDate=2024-12-31
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
